items.title: You can buy Chompie’s Jerusalem Challah Bread at Arizona Costcos
items.summary:
Chompie’s, a true family-owned business and “Arizona’s New York Deli Since 1979” – announced that its new Jerusalem Challah Bread is now available at all Arizona Costco Wholesale stores. The seventeen Costco locations are spread out across the state, including Tucson and Prescott.
